  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aimed to examine the feasibility, usability, user satisfaction, safety, and
      preliminary efficacy of a smartphone application intervention for young adults with
      subthreshold depression.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
